c:T46d,Aframax tankers (80,000–120,000 DWT) are the workhorse of mid-range crude and refined product transport, ideally sized for Atlantic Basin and intra-regional voyages. XRT Group's logistics desk arranges Aframax voyage charters for crude, fuel oil, and clean petroleum products from our Houston and Rotterdam hubs.

**Vessel Specification**

80,000–120,000 DWT, double-hull (MARPOL compliant), coated or uncoated tanks for clean/dirty cargo. All nominated tonnage subject to OCIMF SIRE vetting and CDI inspection where applicable.

**Chartering**

Voyage charter (VC) basis on Worldscale terms, or time charter (TC) for repeat programmes. Current indicative range WS 92–110 on benchmark routes (TD3C, TD7, TD25), subject to bunker prices and position lists.

**Routes**

US Gulf to ARA (TD25), Caribbean to USAC, intra-Mediterranean, and North Sea coastal. Laytime, demurrage, and bunker clauses per ASBATANKVOY or BPVOY4.

**Risk & Compliance**

Vessel sanctions screening (IMO/MMSI cross-check), P&I Club cover verification, AIS continuity monitoring, and charter-party risk structuring through our Risk Mitigation Matrix desk.4:["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 pt-10 sm:pt-16 pb-10 sm:pb-12","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_400px] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"label-caps px-3 py-1.5 border","style":{"color":"#916f6c","borderColor":"#916f6c"},"children":"LOG-001"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"label-caps text-[#A8A5A0]","children":"Logistics Infrastructure"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-[clamp(2.25rem,6vw,4.5rem)] text-white leading-[1.0] mb-4","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-barlow)","fontWeight":900,"letterSpacing":"-0.02em","textTransform":"uppercase"},"children":"Aframax Tanker Charter"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base text-[#A8A5A0] mb-8","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-archivo)","letterSpacing":"0.04em"},"children":"80–120k DWT / Clean or Dirty"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base sm:text-lg text-[#C4C1BE] leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-archivo)"},"children":"Aframax tanker chartering, 80–120k DWT, clean or dirty petroleum cargo, from Houston and Rotterdam. Worldscale-referenced pricing WS 92–110. Voyage charter basis. P&I Club and OCIMF SIRE vetted tonnage."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 border-t border-xrt-steel/15","children":[["$","div","Min. Volume",{"className":"py-5 sm:py-6 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-xrt-steel/15 sm:px-6 sm:first:pl-0","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"label-caps text-[#A8A5A0] mb-2","children":"Min. Volume"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-black text-white","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-barlow)","letterSpacing":"-